content.rendered:
Directed by Gagan Puri

Written by Sandeep Rale

Cast Sonia Albizuri (Miss Jane). Aminnima (Jimmy). Samiksha Bhatt (Ghost / Sanjana). Navid Mirzaaghazadeh((as Iosif Samli)). Yuvraaj Parashar. Deepti Pujari. Jeet Raidutt ((as Jeet Rai Dutt)). Rajesh Sharma. Vedita Pratap Singh. Jaya Virlley ((as Jaya Virle)). Moein z (Singer)

Languages Hindi

Producers Jaspal Singh P. Ghunia. Nitesh Kumar. Jagmeet Singh

Production Peacock Motion Picture. Singh Multimedia Creation
